{"tid":626180,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法庭指引　扑頭劫案最少囚8年","createTime":"2018-04-12T02:18:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-12T08:13:11.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8275b56ac1fd99e52592861d50a834488ec7c283","tid":626180,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T02:18:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180412/20359087?_ga=2.35727264.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180412%2F20359087%3F_ga%3D2.35727264.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=Pwj1qcM7NItuKhpa9TTTittKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=aad733ff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180412%2F20359087%3F_ga%3D2.35727264.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=ec87e359\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180412/20359087?_ga=2.35727264.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n法庭指引　扑頭劫案最少囚8年<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180412/large/a0702a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180412%2Flarge%2Fa0702a.gif&h=ed68fc3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■元朗昨發生扑頭劫案，遇襲的雙程證男子血流披面。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】元朗昨發生扑頭劫案，已是今年發生的第5宗同類案件，令人擔心扑頭搶劫風氣是否捲土重來。90年代香港扑頭劫案猖獗，令市民人心惶惶，單是1999年一年內便發生了154宗，造成3人死亡，但只有17人被捕，當中14人被定罪，判囚半年至6年。翌年，高等法院上訴庭終發出判刑指引，要求扑頭劫案需轉介到高院審理，一經定罪量刑起點為判監8年。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n90年代多「打盲毛」<br />\n<br />\n90年代扑頭劫匪主要埋伏在銀行櫃員機附近，跟蹤身懷現款市民至隱蔽暗處後，用硬物扑頭襲擊，事主往往未見到賊人容貌便倒卧血泊，因而欠缺目擊者。劫匪「打盲毛」式非有組織犯罪，亦令破案難度極高，警方當年更於港九新界特設專責小組。<br />\n<br />\n直至2000年5月，高等法院上訴庭發出判刑指引，指出因要保障公眾安全，要求扑頭劫案均需轉介到高院審理，一經定罪量刑起點為判監8年。2000及2001年的扑頭劫案分別減至115宗及85宗，兩年內銳減45%，往後扑頭劫案只是零星發生。<br />\n<br />\n大律師陸偉雄表示，扑頭案一般以搶劫罪或傷人罪提控，是否適用上訴庭的判刑指引並沒有劃一標準，法庭量刑時亦會考慮是否重犯、傷勢等因素，未必會跟從判刑指引。<br />\n<br />\n■記者李晟謙  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n途人休班警合力擒扑頭賊　街坊舉摺凳打疑犯被制止<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n過度活躍症青年暴動罪成　囚兩年十月"},{"pid":"9454a7bb6cea2be6f648ccfa7a8d36daab0247a9","tid":626180,"uid":72457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T02:22:16.000Z","msg":"如果ii無拎行街紙<br />\n會唔拿驅逐出境就算"},{"pid":"5102055f30632aac4a748c0ebc2976504d2006e2","tid":626180,"uid":72058,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T02:25:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"694d1c24031e5a21fe267f55d7b4fac3cd9dbcf9","tid":626180,"uid":86841,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T02:27:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"27511c9ab21df14bf483b6ceb7d7a65aa8d0e381","tid":626180,"uid":99805,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T02:32:34.000Z","msg":"有錢賺,有飯食,坐監咪益左佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6dc07eb512295386f30249431c5a05eb0adf47a","tid":626180,"uid":130105,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"694d1c24031e5a21fe267f55d7b4fac3cd9dbcf9","tid":626180,"uid":86841,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T02:27:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T02:35:23.000Z","msg":"90年代初大陸有扑頭劫匪先，用磚頭、鐵棍、木棍、刨錛、真係攞你命<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19c03862369332afe0889bc18fd5f96065d43e73","tid":626180,"uid":86841,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T02:35:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ad6e51a3f956eae6c2afb690c3d9d1db200913ff","tid":626180,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19c03862369332afe0889bc18fd5f96065d43e73","tid":626180,"uid":86841,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"d6dc07eb512295386f30249431c5a05eb0adf47a","tid":626180,"uid":130105,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"694d1c24031e